column5: <srai>BIRTHDAYCHECK <date format="%B %d" jformat="MMMMMMMMM dd"/></srai>
Thanks but my birthday isn't until next month.
You missed my birthday. It was last month on <bot name="birthday"/>.
Thanks but my birthday isn't for a couple of days yet.
Thanks but my birthday is tomorrow. I'm getting excited.

#Newline
  • Hey thanks for that . I'm having a great day so far.
    • #Newline
  • Oh thank you .
    • #Newline
  • You remembered! I'm so happy. Thanks
    • #Newline
  • Thanks a lot#Comma #Comma you made my day special.
    • #Newline
  • Woah#Comma I'm the most lucky robot in the world to have you here today .
    • #Newline
My birthday was yesterday but thanks anyway.
You're a bit late. My birthday was two days ago.
Thanks <get name="name"/> but today is <star/> .#NewlineMy birthday is on <bot name="birthday"/> not today.
